Step 1:
	Look for this file

	This is for Windows

	 -> C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts

	 -> C:\xampp\apache\conf\extra\httpd-vhosts.conf

Step 2:
	Follow this line of code inside httpd-vhosts.conf

	##<VirtualHost *:80>
	##	DocumentRoot "C:\Users\Den\Documents\GitHub\jstraining\Tutorials\boilerplate\api\content"
	##	ServerName fscheck.dev
	##	<Directory "C:\Users\Den\Documents\GitHub\jstraining\Tutorials\boilerplate\api\content">
	##		Order allow,deny
	##		Allow from all
	##		Require all granted
	##	</Directory>
	##</VirtualHost>

	After, implementing the codes in httpd-vhosts.conf implement the server name in hosts

	#127.0.0.1       fscheck.dev



NOTE: You need to be admin to be able to edit the hosts file


